rows.label: tlk41300021_01_msg0001
rows.name:
Running a shop here, you get to
hear all sorts of interesting gossip.

rows.label: tlk41300021_01_msg0002
rows.name:
It's right by the port, so we get to see
a lot of adventurers and merchants.

rows.label: tlk41300021_01_msg0003
rows.name:
For instance, did you know every
Divine Beast has a few out-of-the-way spots
known as Secret Areas?

rows.label: tlk41300021_01_msg0004
rows.name:
In Gula, for instance, there's a place
called Dawnview Grotto which has the
most exquisite view you ever saw.

rows.label: tlk41300021_01_msg0005
rows.name:
Part of the thrill of adventuring is
seeking out the kinds of places and
views that make you really feel alive!
